modName: vwr Draugr Translator lol - NSFW audio
summary: This is an alternative, NSFW voice replacer for Draugr.
descriptionHtml:
After seeing the current Draugr Voice replacer by vladdyvostok, I decided I wanted to try something similar with voice acted Draugr. The sounds came out okay, but unfortunately Draugr don\'t talk very much so in the 5 hours of testing I\'ve done, I\'ve only gotten a few samples recorded in the video. Check it out, download and endorse, and drop by http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/37725//? to credit vladdy for the funny idea!
